==Indonesian==

===Adjective===
''bokep ''
#(pornographic film) - originated from abbreviation BF which means Blue Film. BF is read Beh-Ef, which in its pidgin form is read as Beh-Ep. The [[prokem]] word Bokep is obtained by inserting ok in between Beh-Ep.

===Verb===
''bokep''
#to watch pornography.

====Transformation====
*'''ngebokep''': Active Intransitive Verb using affix '''me-V'''
